@Aaron Vontell <!subteam^SQ3KR3V17|@Software Engineers> making sure that the front end handles everything the same is exactly the QA + Development + testing activity we're about go undergo. Even though /in theory/ it's all the same, we have to navigate the fact that `page image != record` in terms of bits on disk... e.g., when a record is 2 pages, we need to make sure the front-end is showing the right two pages, visually, to the user.

We're looking for examples of flows that use interesting Map Records steps.

Have you ever written a flow with a custom mapper? A link to that flow is exactly what we're looking for
